119
00:16:15,039 --> 00:16:17,580
[SPEAKER_00] To se sve češće i češće spominje u medijima.

120
00:16:17,580 --> 00:16:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] I kakve to posljedice može imati na ostatak svijeta i na Europu,

121
00:16:21,940 --> 00:16:25,120
[SPEAKER_00] tu recimo kod nas, u susjedstvu Kina, Tajvan?

122
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:31,500
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja mislim da, uvodno smo kazali da je ovaj rat prekretnica popuno toga,

123
00:16:31,500 --> 00:16:37,919
