140
00:17:37,900 --> 00:17:40,460
[SPEAKER_01] On je nestao sa scene. Nestao.

141
00:17:40,460 --> 00:17:46,299
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, negdje, dakle, vojna sociologija nas opet moralna uči,

142
00:17:46,299 --> 00:17:48,839
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda vojna sociologija se svačin bave,

143
00:17:48,839 --> 00:17:51,400
[SPEAKER_01] pa i među ostalo se bave analizama i sukoba.

144
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:57,160
