273
00:23:58,539 --> 00:24:01,500
[SPEAKER_01] I da to nije jedini kriterij,

274
00:24:01,500 --> 00:24:03,420
[SPEAKER_01] da nije jedini kriterij.

275
00:24:03,420 --> 00:24:04,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što je u ratu,

276
