00:38:03,079 --> 00:38:03,699
[SPEAKER_00] okej,

962
00:38:03,699 --> 00:38:04,920
[SPEAKER_00] svatko ima pravo na svoju,

963
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:05,159
[SPEAKER_00] ali,

964
00:38:05,159 --> 00:38:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] pa to vam je...

965
00:38:05,920 --> 00:38:07,079
[SPEAKER_00] A situacija oko nas,

966
00:38:07,079 --> 00:38:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] i sami ste rekli,

967
00:38:07,960 --> 00:38:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] ne znao vi,

968
00:38:08,380 --> 00:38:09,860
[SPEAKER_00] je vrlo, vrlo ozbiljna.

969
00:38:09,860 --> 00:38:10,159
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

970
00:38:10,159 --> 00:38:12,320
[SPEAKER_01] to vam je uvijek tipično,

971
00:38:12,420 --> 00:38:14,539
[SPEAKER_01] jeli, te reakcije su razumljive.

972
00:38:14,539 --> 00:38:17,679
[SPEAKER_01] I zašto su razumljive?

973
00:38:17,679 --> 00:38:19,539
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što sigurnostom je jedan,

974
00:38:19,539 --> 00:38:21,460
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo, kako bih ja rekao,

975
00:38:21,460 --> 00:38:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] jedan nevjerojatno kompleksan fenomen,

976
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:25,800
[SPEAKER_01] teorijski,

977
00:38:25,800 --> 00:38:27,019
[SPEAKER_01] ali i empirijski.

978
00:38:27,019 --> 00:38:28,079
[SPEAKER_01] Jel?

979
00:38:28,079 --> 00:38:29,119
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

980
00:38:29,119 --> 00:38:30,019
[SPEAKER_01] i

981
00:38:30,019 --> 00:38:33,820
[SPEAKER_01] fon ima jednu svoju specifičnost,

982
00:38:33,820 --> 00:38:34,579
[SPEAKER_01] šta to je,

983
00:38:34,579 --> 00:38:35,860
[SPEAKER_01] da,

984
00:38:35,860 --> 00:38:36,840
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj,

985
00:38:36,840 --> 00:38:39,360
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek imamo relativističke stave,

986
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:40,619
[SPEAKER_01] prema sigurnosti,

987
00:38:40,619 --> 00:38:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] jel?

988
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:42,260
[SPEAKER_01] Samo,

989
00:38:42,260 --> 00:38:44,599
[SPEAKER_01] ako odnemo u ovu svakodnenu populaciju,

990
00:38:44,599 --> 00:38:47,360
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek imamo relativizaciju rizika.

991
00:38:47,360 --> 00:38:48,019
[SPEAKER_01] Neće mene.

992
00:38:48,019 --> 00:38:48,739
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

993
00:38:48,739 --> 00:38:49,579
[SPEAKER_01] Neće, jel?

994
00:38:49,579 --> 00:38:50,639
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro,

995
00:38:50,639 --> 00:38:51,199
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj,

996
00:38:51,199 --> 00:38:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] imamo neki način ignoriranje rizika,

997
00:38:54,000 --> 00:38:54,380
[SPEAKER_01] jel?

998
00:38:54,380 --> 00:38:55,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ono što,

999
00:38:55,699 --> 00:38:56,280
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj,

1000
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:57,320
[SPEAKER_01] s druge strane,

1001
00:38:57,320 --> 00:39:00,360
[SPEAKER_01] ne pobitno znamo što je sigurnost,

1002
00:39:00,940 --> 00:39:02,559
[SPEAKER_01] a to je empirijski,

1003
00:39:02,559 --> 00:39:03,500
[SPEAKER_01] onda kada izgubimo.

1004
00:39:03,500 --> 00:39:05,539
[SPEAKER_01] E, onda više nikog ne pita.

1005
00:39:05,539 --> 00:39:08,460
[SPEAKER_01] E, zato sigurnost ima sasvim drugu ulogu,

1006
00:39:08,460 --> 00:39:09,079
[SPEAKER_01] jel?

1007
00:39:09,079 --> 00:39:10,579
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, da je ne izgubimo.

1008
00:39:10,579 --> 00:39:15,380
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, sigurnost u svojoj biti je temeljna socijalna potreba.

1009
00:39:15,380 --> 00:39:17,159
[SPEAKER_01] Temeljna socijalna potreba.

1010
00:39:17,159 --> 00:39:19,679
[SPEAKER_01] To znači što je jedan znameniti kancelar,

1011
00:39:19,679 --> 00:39:20,900
[SPEAKER_01] još pređe 80 godina,

1012
00:39:20,900 --> 00:39:22,300
[SPEAKER_01] kada Aden Auer kazao,

1013
00:39:22,300 --> 00:39:23,880
[SPEAKER_01] sigurnost nije sve,

1014
00:39:23,880 --> 00:39:25,900
[SPEAKER_01] ali sve ostalo bez sigurnosti je ništa.

1015
00:39:25,900 --> 00:39:26,219
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1016
00:39:26,219 --> 00:39:29,579
[SPEAKER_01] I ja bih rekao da je to ne pobitnom polazište,

1017
00:39:30,119 --> 00:39:31,800
[SPEAKER_01] a da sve ostalo vam je stvar,

1018
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:32,760
[SPEAKER_01] ja bih rekao,

1019
00:39:32,760 --> 00:39:33,900
[SPEAKER_01] prvo ekspertiza,

1020
00:39:33,900 --> 00:39:35,519
[SPEAKER_01] ali i tehnika,

1021
00:39:35,519 --> 00:39:38,139
[SPEAKER_01] ali i svačanja svega toga zajedla.

1022
00:39:38,139 --> 00:39:39,599
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, svačanja, jel?

1023
00:39:39,599 --> 00:39:43,079
[SPEAKER_01] I onda imate postupne,

1024
00:39:43,079 --> 00:39:43,920
[SPEAKER_01] ja bih rekao,

1025
00:39:43,920 --> 00:39:47,239
[SPEAKER_01] modele za implementaciju toga.

1026
00:39:47,239 --> 00:39:49,199
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek vam je to spoj,

1027
00:39:49,199 --> 00:39:49,639
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1028
00:39:49,639 --> 00:39:50,539
[SPEAKER_01] edukacije,

1029
00:39:50,539 --> 00:39:51,880
[SPEAKER_01] jednog tipa,

1030
00:39:51,880 --> 00:39:52,239
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1031
00:39:52,239 --> 00:39:53,500
[SPEAKER_01] znamstveno-teorijskog,

1032
00:39:53,500 --> 00:39:53,619
[SPEAKER_01] jel?

1033
00:39:53,619 --> 00:39:55,280
[SPEAKER_01] i drugo od treninga,

1034
00:39:55,280 --> 00:39:55,500
[SPEAKER_01] jel?

1035
00:39:55,500 --> 00:39:56,719
[SPEAKER_01] I naravno,

1036
00:39:56,719 --> 00:39:58,519
[SPEAKER_01] da bi to sve skupa mogli napraviti,

1037
00:39:58,519 --> 00:39:59,639
[SPEAKER_01] morate ima razvoj svijesti.

1038
00:39:59,639 --> 00:40:01,260
[SPEAKER_01] Razvoj svijesti.

1039
00:40:01,260 --> 00:40:02,980
[SPEAKER_01] Najteže je razviti svijest,

1040
00:40:02,980 --> 00:40:04,500
[SPEAKER_01] jer naravno da,

1041
00:40:04,500 --> 00:40:05,079
[SPEAKER_01] ha, gledajte,

1042
00:40:05,079 --> 00:40:06,679
[SPEAKER_01] što bi ja sad ulagao u sigurnost

1043
00:40:06,679 --> 00:40:07,440
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam siguran?

1044
00:40:07,519 --> 00:40:08,360
[SPEAKER_01] To su vam tipični,

1045
00:40:08,360 --> 00:40:10,559
[SPEAKER_01] ignoransko-aroganski pristup

1046
00:40:10,559 --> 00:40:11,860
[SPEAKER_01] i pojedinaca i društva.

1047
00:40:11,860 --> 00:40:13,139
[SPEAKER_01] Uzmite firme,

1048
00:40:13,139 --> 00:40:13,820
[SPEAKER_01] ako hoćete,

1049
00:40:13,820 --> 00:40:13,960
[SPEAKER_01] jel?

1050
00:40:13,960 --> 00:40:15,539
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek vam je sukop,

1051
00:40:15,539 --> 00:40:15,760
[SPEAKER_01] jel?

1052
00:40:15,760 --> 00:40:16,960
[SPEAKER_01] Sada se pojavilo nešto

1053
00:40:16,960 --> 00:40:17,659
[SPEAKER_01] što je logično,

1054
00:40:17,659 --> 00:40:17,800
[SPEAKER_01] jel?

1055
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:19,179
[SPEAKER_01] Zadnjih desetljedeća što se zove

1056
00:40:19,179 --> 00:40:21,239
[SPEAKER_01] poslovna ili korporativna sigurnost.

1057
00:40:21,239 --> 00:40:21,599
[SPEAKER_01] Sigurno, da.

1058
00:40:21,599 --> 00:40:22,019
[SPEAKER_01] Jel?

1059
00:40:22,019 --> 00:40:22,880
[SPEAKER_01] To je, dakle,

1060
00:40:22,880 --> 00:40:24,679
[SPEAKER_01] presudno za sigurnost poslovanja.

1061
00:40:24,679 --> 00:40:25,659
[SPEAKER_01] To penedžeri kaže,

1062
00:40:25,659 --> 00:40:26,079
[SPEAKER_01] znači što?

1063
00:40:26,079 --> 00:40:27,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ma to je bez veze,

1064
00:40:27,480 --> 00:40:28,719
[SPEAKER_01] to je od uzimanja profita.

1065
00:40:28,719 --> 00:40:29,619
[SPEAKER_01] Vita, nama ništa nije,

1066
00:40:37,519 --> 00:40:37,900
[SPEAKER_01] po mir,

1067
00:40:37,900 --> 00:40:39,019
[SPEAKER_01] ta dva suprotna stajališta.

1068
00:40:39,019 --> 00:40:39,860
[SPEAKER_01] To, to, to.

1069
00:40:39,860 --> 00:40:41,340
[SPEAKER_01] E, to vam je i na razini društva,

1070
00:40:41,340 --> 00:40:41,739
[SPEAKER_01] gledajte,

1071
00:40:41,739 --> 00:40:43,219
[SPEAKER_01] onda se morate baviti time,

1072
00:40:43,219 --> 00:40:44,559
[SPEAKER_01] ja bih rekao,

1073
00:40:44,559 --> 00:40:45,480
[SPEAKER_01] puno subtilnije,

1074
00:40:45,480 --> 00:40:46,019
[SPEAKER_01] puno nije,

1075
00:40:46,019 --> 00:40:46,679
[SPEAKER_01] si ranije,

1076
00:40:46,679 --> 00:40:48,039
[SPEAKER_01] na prvom mjestu edukacija.

1077
00:40:48,039 --> 00:40:49,179
[SPEAKER_01] A zamislite sad.

1078
00:40:49,179 --> 00:40:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] To je edukacija.

1079
00:40:50,119 --> 00:40:51,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znate, danas odete na zapad,

1080
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] vi danas nemate na seučilištu

1081
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] ni jednom,

1082
00:40:54,000 --> 00:40:54,420
[SPEAKER_01] jel?

1083
00:40:54,420 --> 00:40:55,579
[SPEAKER_01] U svijetu ozbiljnom,

1084
00:40:55,579 --> 00:40:56,659
[SPEAKER_01] da nemate neki program

1085
00:40:56,659 --> 00:40:59,219
[SPEAKER_01] iz svere prototerorizma.

1086
00:40:59,219 --> 00:40:59,480
[UNKNOWN] Da.

1087
00:40:59,480 --> 00:41:00,840
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to je normalno,

1088
00:41:00,840 --> 00:41:01,159
[SPEAKER_01] gledajte,

1089
00:41:01,239 --> 00:41:02,539
[SPEAKER_01] terorizam pogađa svakoga.

1090
00:41:02,539 --> 00:41:03,760
[SPEAKER_01] Svakoga.

1091
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:05,880
[SPEAKER_01] Terorizam je civilno područje.

1092
00:41:05,880 --> 00:41:08,340
[SPEAKER_01] Jel, to vam daleko ode,

1093
00:41:08,340 --> 00:41:09,400
[SPEAKER_01] sad što nešto,

1094
00:41:09,400 --> 00:41:10,659
[SPEAKER_01] koliko vam to daleko ode,

1095
00:41:10,659 --> 00:41:12,099
[SPEAKER_01] sad da sam ja i neka profesora

1096
00:41:12,099 --> 00:41:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] studija terorizma,

1097
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:14,780
[SPEAKER_01] pa ponešto malo znam,

1098
00:41:14,780 --> 00:41:15,519
[SPEAKER_01] jel,

1099
00:41:15,519 --> 00:41:16,980
[SPEAKER_01] najveći postadak,

1100
00:41:16,980 --> 00:41:18,099
[SPEAKER_01] dvije trećine terorista

1101
00:41:18,099 --> 00:41:19,139
[SPEAKER_01] vam postanu teroristi

1102
00:41:19,139 --> 00:41:20,500
[SPEAKER_01] u procesu na socijalizaciji

1103
00:41:20,500 --> 00:41:21,360
[SPEAKER_01] u fakultetskoj dobi.

1104
00:41:21,360 --> 00:41:24,619
[SPEAKER_01] U fakultetskoj dobi.

1105
00:41:24,619 --> 00:41:25,960
[SPEAKER_01] Pa onda je logično

1106
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:26,920
[SPEAKER_01] da fakulteti

1107
00:41:26,920 --> 00:41:29,360
[SPEAKER_01] imaju i kao organizacije,

1108
00:41:29,360 --> 00:41:31,159
[SPEAKER_01] ali u smislu ovog temeljnog biznisa,

1109
00:41:31,239 --> 00:41:32,800
[SPEAKER_01] kor biznisa ulogu

1110
00:41:32,800 --> 00:41:34,360
[SPEAKER_01] dakle u prototerorizmu.

1111
00:41:34,360 --> 00:41:36,480
[SPEAKER_01] I fakulteti su i mete.

1112
00:41:36,480 --> 00:41:37,219
[SPEAKER_01] Vrlo, vrlo.

1113
00:41:37,219 --> 00:41:38,039
[SPEAKER_01] Privlašte.

1114
00:41:38,039 --> 00:41:38,360
[SPEAKER_01] Svašta.

1115
00:41:38,360 --> 00:41:38,920
[SPEAKER_01] Svašta.

1116
00:41:38,920 --> 00:41:41,619
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su svašta.

1117
00:41:41,619 --> 00:41:42,460
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je logično,

1118
00:41:42,460 --> 00:41:42,860
[SPEAKER_01] ali da,

1119
00:41:42,860 --> 00:41:44,780
[SPEAKER_01] najprije morate razvijaći svijest

1120
00:41:44,780 --> 00:41:46,780
[SPEAKER_01] da smo ugroženi.

1121
00:41:46,780 --> 00:41:48,179
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sigurnost vam je

1122
00:41:48,179 --> 00:41:50,960
[SPEAKER_01] u tom smislu specifična,

1123
00:41:50,960 --> 00:41:52,860
[SPEAKER_01] jer jedino kad znamo

1124
00:41:52,860 --> 00:41:54,340
[SPEAKER_01] da nemamo sigurnost

1125
00:41:54,340 --> 00:41:55,519
[SPEAKER_01] ili postajemo svijestni

1126
00:41:55,519 --> 00:41:56,340
[SPEAKER_01] što je sigurnost,

1127
00:41:56,340 --> 00:41:57,039
[SPEAKER_01] to je kad izgubim,

1128
00:41:57,039 --> 00:41:57,719
[SPEAKER_01] onda je kasno.

1129
00:41:57,719 --> 00:41:59,519
[SPEAKER_01] Zato sigurnosti je,

1130
00:41:59,519 --> 00:42:00,659
[SPEAKER_01] dakle,

1131
00:42:00,760 --> 00:42:02,500
[SPEAKER_01] zato postoji država,

1132
00:42:02,500 --> 00:42:04,400
[SPEAKER_01] temeljna funkcija države

1133
00:42:04,400 --> 00:42:05,719
[SPEAKER_01] je funkcija sigurnosti.

1134
00:42:05,719 --> 00:42:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bez funkcije sigurnosti

1135
00:42:07,000 --> 00:42:07,800
[SPEAKER_01] nema države.

1136
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:09,860
[SPEAKER_01] Po svim ostalim atributima

1137
00:42:09,860 --> 00:42:11,199
[SPEAKER_01] države se mogu razlikovati,

1138
00:42:11,199 --> 00:42:11,920
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne po ome.

1139
00:42:11,920 --> 00:42:12,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ali država,

1140
00:42:12,659 --> 00:42:13,019
[SPEAKER_01] naravno,

1141
00:42:13,019 --> 00:42:13,500
[SPEAKER_01] nije sve.

1142
00:42:13,500 --> 00:42:15,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to temeljna funkcija države

1143
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:16,960
[SPEAKER_01] koja ukazuje na to

1144
00:42:16,960 --> 00:42:18,659
[SPEAKER_01] što je sigurnost.

1145
00:42:18,659 --> 00:42:20,519
[SPEAKER_01] Zato sigurnosti jeste,

1146
00:42:20,519 --> 00:42:22,159
[SPEAKER_01] nema nikakve dileme,

1147
00:42:22,159 --> 00:42:23,699
[SPEAKER_01] najorganiziranija

1148
00:42:23,699 --> 00:42:25,179
[SPEAKER_01] društvena djelatnost,

1149
00:42:25,179 --> 00:42:27,159
[SPEAKER_01] sa različitim dimenzijama

1150
00:42:27,159 --> 00:42:28,460
[SPEAKER_01] organiziranosti,

1151
00:42:28,820 --> 00:42:30,420
[SPEAKER_01] u svim područjima.

1152
00:42:30,420 --> 00:42:32,099
[SPEAKER_01] Pa onda to nije samo

1153
00:42:32,099 --> 00:42:33,980
[SPEAKER_01] odgovornost države.

1154
00:42:33,980 --> 00:42:35,599
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da,

1155
00:42:35,599 --> 00:42:36,960
[SPEAKER_01] ja bih rekao da,

1156
00:42:36,960 --> 00:42:40,340
[SPEAKER_01] to nam treba.

1157
00:42:40,739 --> 00:42:41,739
[SPEAKER_00] A zamislite vi sad

1158
00:42:41,739 --> 00:42:42,920
[SPEAKER_00] uvijest u osnovne škole

1159
00:42:42,920 --> 00:42:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] onoj DSZ šta smo mi imali?

1160
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:46,179
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja nisam zauđenje

1161
00:42:46,179 --> 00:42:47,400
[SPEAKER_01] za onoj DSZ,

1162
00:42:47,400 --> 00:42:48,119
[SPEAKER_01] ali to su ti,

1163
00:42:48,119 --> 00:42:49,500
[SPEAKER_01] malo prvi smo spomenuli,

1164
00:42:49,500 --> 00:42:50,300
[SPEAKER_01] neke odjume

1165
00:42:50,300 --> 00:42:51,619
[SPEAKER_01] prema pijućem sistemu,

1166
00:42:51,619 --> 00:42:53,239
[SPEAKER_01] što su razumljivi sistemi,

1167
00:42:53,239 --> 00:42:53,940
[SPEAKER_01] razumljivi,

1168
00:42:53,940 --> 00:42:54,579
[SPEAKER_01] ali neki,

1169
00:42:54,579 --> 00:42:55,960
[SPEAKER_01] pogotovo neki nas,

1170
00:42:55,960 --> 00:42:57,300
[SPEAKER_01] prijevazni generacija,

1171
00:42:57,300 --> 00:42:57,980
[SPEAKER_01] to je razumljivo.

1172
00:42:57,980 --> 00:42:59,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ali jedno su,

1173
00:42:59,960 --> 00:43:00,960
[SPEAKER_01] ja bih rekao,

1174
00:43:00,960 --> 00:43:01,780
[SPEAKER_01] ideološko,

1175
